<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>footer window</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset_plus.css">

    <style>
        .clearfix::after {
            content: "";
            display: block;
            clear: both;
        }
    </style>

    <!-- footer 버튼 4개 회사소개, 이용약관, 개인정보처리방침, 이용안내 -->
     <style>
        #footer_navi_container{
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        #footer_navi_container>ul{
            width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        #footer_navi_container>ul>li{
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            margin-right: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            line-height: 60px;
        }
        #footer_navi_container>ul>li::before{
            content: '';
            width: 1px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #797979;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            right: -30px;
        }
     </style>

    <!-- footer 하단 정보 -->
    <style>
        #footer_company_info_container{
            width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        #footer_company_info_container>p{
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #797979;
            margin-left: 43px;
        }
        #company_info span{
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        #cs_info{
            width: 220px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        #cs_info .btn-info{
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        #cs_info .btn-info>a{
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            width: 104px;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="footer_container">
        <div id="footer_navi_container">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="">회사소개</a></li>
                <li><a href="">이용약관</a></li>
                <li><a href="">개인정보처리방침</a></li>
                <li><a href="">이용안내</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div id="footer_company_info_container" class="clearfix">
                
            <a class="fleft" href="" ><img src="images/logo.png" alt="logo"></a>
            <p class="fleft">
                <span>(주) 퓨어셀코리아 </span><br>
                <span> 대표자 : 김철호 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 사업자 등록번호 : 411-81-92320 </span><br>
                <span>통신판매업 신고번호 : 2020-서울강남-02095 [사업자정보확인] </span><br>
                <span>주소 : 서울특별시 강남구 학동로101길 26 (청담동) 211호개인정보관리책임자 : 이진희 </span><br><br>
                
                Copyright © PURESELL 퓨어셀. All rights reserved.
            </p>

            <div id="cs_info" class="fright">
                <h3 style="font: 18px;">CS CENTER 1599-8604</h3>
                <p>
                    평일 10:00 - 17:00 <br>
                    (점심시간 : 12:00 - 13:00) <br>
                    ​토.일.공휴일 휴무 <br>
                </p>
                <div class="btn-info">
                    <a href="">1:1 문의하기</a>
                    <a href="">자주 묻는 질문</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>